README
This assumes that the filenames are in the format: PROJECT ID ANIMAL ID TISSUE TIMEPOINT ACCESSION NUMBER STAIN
Works with timepoints that are in the format: (value) (units) or (units) (value)
Also works with non numerical timepoints such as Early Dead (E.D.) and Not Applicable (NA)
Launch the script
Pick yor files
Pick how you want to stratify them
GO!
